<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/BDJ.11.e113290.figure2>
    dc:description "Figure 2. Dissected bulb of Liphistius liz sp. nov., holotype male. A prodorsal view; B ventral view. Abbreviations: CT, contrategulum; E, embolus; PeP, paraembolic plate; ST subtegulum; T, tegulum, vp, ventral process of contrategulum." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/911497" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/BDJ.11.e113290.figure4>
    dc:description "Figure 4. Palp of Liphistius liz sp. nov., holotype male. A dorsal view; B retrolateral view; C ventral view; D clavate trichobothria. Abbreviations: cu, cumulus; PC, paracymbium; TiA, tibial apophysis." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/911501" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/BDJ.11.e113290.figure5>
    dc:description "Figure 5. Vulva of Liphistius liz sp. nov., paratype female. A dorsal view; B ventral view. Abbreviations: ALP, anterolateral protuberance on poreplate; BM, bulging margin on ventral poreplate; CDO, central dorsal opening; DOP, dorsal opening of posterolateral protuberance on poreplate; GA, genital atrium; PLP, posterolateral protuberance on poreplate; PPl, poreplate; PS, posterior stalk; RC, receptacular cluster." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/911502" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/BDJ.11.e113290.figure6>
    dc:description "Figure 6. Vulvae of Liphistius liz sp. nov., paratype females. A, C dorsal view; B, D ventral view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/911503" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/BDJ.11.e113290.figure7>
    dc:description "Figure 7. Habitus of Liphistius liz sp. nov., dorsal view. A holotype male; B paratype female." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/911504" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/BDJ.11.e113290.figure8>
    dc:description "Figure 8. Distribution records of Liphistius from China. 1 L. nabang; 2 L. liz sp. nov." ;
